headline: Equinix Nigeria And Japan Moves Test Market View On Valuation
summary: Equinix is expanding in Nigeria as part of a $100 million Africa-wide investment initiative in the data center sector. The company is positioning itself as a key enabler of Nigeria's fast-growing data center and digital infrastructure market. In Japan, Equinix is partnering with Trafficmind.com to host an expanded Anycast edge presence in Osaka. The collaboration in Osaka is intended to support edge network capacity and regulatory compliant workloads across Asia-Pacific. For investors...

headline: McKay Brothers and Quincy Data Expand Best-in-Class Cross-Border Market Interconnection Between Ontario and the US
summary: McKay Brothers, a global provider of fast connectivity between financial market venues, and its sister company Quincy Data, a distributor of time-sensitive market data, have expanded services linking key Canadian financial markets with major US trading hubs in Illinois and New Jersey.
